Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.86,0:00:08.26,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,None are left who know me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:11.48,Chiha-main,Yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:13.84,Chiha-main,Yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:20.17,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Impassionate gods...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.45,0:00:27.74,Chiha-title,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1700,0)}Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:37.07,Chiha-ep-title-verse,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1000)}Verse 23
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:37.07,Chiha-ep-title-poem,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1000)}The \NNight \NIs \NNearly \NPast
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:39.68,Chiha-main,Yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto Yumi: won by four cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:41.14,Chiha-main,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yumin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.55,0:01:43.74,Chiha-main,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You're well on your way to \Nreclaiming the title of Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:45.58,GE,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,1)}Great Expectations
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:47.48,Chiha-main,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Get plenty of rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:50.11,Chiha-main,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to play four more matches \Nbefore you reach the final!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.49,0:01:52.90,Chiha-internal,Yumi,0000,0000,0000,,So much pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:55.94,Chiha-internal,Yumi,0000,0000,0000,,But if there weren't any expectations,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:57.34,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have run away already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:09.38,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:12.88,Chiha-internal,Yumi,0000,0000,0000,,I won't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:17.24,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?  Get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:19.19,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Please come out, Chihaya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:20.83,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase, I have chocolate for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:23.62,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about cheering for \NYumin the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:26.97,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:29.10,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that beautiful \Ngirls look better bald.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:33.89,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave my e-mail address, \Nso send me an "after" picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:36.41,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Sudo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:40.09,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We'll shave our heads, so spare Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.38,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:43.30,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm willing to cut my hair really short!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:45.32,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You stay out of it, Kana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:47.61,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:51.43,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever loses first has \Nto shave their head?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.43,0:02:53.15,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan's so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:56.67,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,We know!  Our captain is stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:03:01.26,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Then Sudo-kun, if I beat you, \Nthe bet is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:06.43,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe that you're my \Nopponent in the third round.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:09.36,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning on losing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:11.33,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,If not, we'll run into \Neach other at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.26,0:03:15.20,Chiha-main,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,You better not lose before we play.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.75,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Worry more about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:20.83,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:22.07,Chiha-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.14,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll shave my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:23.84,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:24.92,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I said it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:27.26,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I probably look fine with a \Nshaved head, so I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:28.92,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look better than you will!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:33.61,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is she asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:35.56,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what normally happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:37.21,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,It's been an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:39.06,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:42.07,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You can go back downstairs, Nishida.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:44.40,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You need to cheer for Yamamoto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:48.26,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay here, so Oe-san \Nand Komano can also go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:50.34,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stay here with you-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:05.89,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:12.35,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,She can't sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:28.83,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, Arata says he's won his \Nthird round match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:34.32,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm mail buddies with Arata now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:39.75,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to give you his address \Nonce the qualifiers were over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.06,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:48.64,cellphone,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Got through the third round.\N How's Chihaya doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:48.45,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,He's really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:04.57,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Harada and Sudo-san both won,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:06.08,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,and they're playing each \Nother in the fourth round!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:08.04,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go cheer for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:15.03,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:17.63,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go cheer him on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:20.59,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:26.93,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I know how much it hurts to \Nlose after trying your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:29.87,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to face anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:32.83,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I know how it feels,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:36.60,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,but my words won't be able to reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:41.03,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Only Arata can help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:49.99,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:55.95,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You have to go watch \NDr. Harada and Sudo-san play!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.57,0:05:59.25,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Next year, they'll be \Nyour rivals in Class A!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:02.55,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You have to go watch them \Nplay, not cheer them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:05.98,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:09.51,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,The prez stayed behind because \Nhe was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.77,0:06:11.68,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:12.88,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:15.25,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.69,0:06:16.96,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:24.32,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:28.01,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hopelessly in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.45,people,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Sudo Akita
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:31.37,people,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Harada Hidehiro
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:32.87,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:37.50,Chiha-main,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,He's so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:43.90,Chiha-internal,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,His knees are starting to give.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.34,Chiha-internal,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,I should go easy on him \Nsince he's getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:50.60,Chiha-internal,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,Except, I'm not in a position to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:56.50,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want her to contest every card,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:58.76,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,so I started moving \Nfaster than I needed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.47,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,That was a tactic I never knew about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.98,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:06.97,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:08.37,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:11.04,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you're cold, so put it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:20.65,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was cheering \Nwatching outside, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:22.43,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:25.00,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,It was pretty warm during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:30.71,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,They were standing outside \Nthe entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:34.34,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:36.33,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:43.66,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I lost because I was \Ntoo focused on myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.17,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:48.43,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Harada!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:54.56,Chiha-internal,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,I lost by three cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:56.77,Chiha-internal,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,He's not human...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:07:58.95,Chiha-internal,Sudo,0000,0000,0000,,He's an intelligent bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.20,roar,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,1)}Roar
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.34,0:08:01.51,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Harada!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:04.76,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for saving Ayase's hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:06.71,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?  What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:07.80,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:10.23,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:12.76,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,He only cared about his own victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:13.68,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,He never changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:23.88,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan, you didn't thank \Nyour opponent after the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.34,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,That was wrong of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:28.65,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how upset you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:30.44,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you must thank your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:33.18,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:35.67,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The semi-finals will \Nbegin in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:37.77,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Will the players will please step inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:39.58,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:42.76,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Only two more wins...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:46.96,Chiha-main,Hara,0000,0000,0000,,Two more wins...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:58.96,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Harada lost a close \Nmatch in the semi-finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:03.42,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The Eastern finalists this year \Nare Tsuboguchi Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:06.75,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,from the Shiranami society \Nfor the Master match,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:11.52,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,and Yamamoto Yumi from the Suihoku \Nsociety for the Queen match.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:14.35,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,In one month,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:18.30,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll be playing a \Nbest-of-three match
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:20.43,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,against the Western finalists
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:22.99,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,for the right to challenge\N the Master and Queen in January.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:26.31,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Kanai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:29.73,Chiha-main,Kanai,0000,0000,0000,,See you next year, rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:32.89,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The long day is finally over,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:36.13,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,and the rest of us will spend \Nthe next year as losers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:45.60,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:49.62,Chiha-main,Wata,0000,0000,0000,,I see you every morning here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:52.28,Chiha-main,Wata,0000,0000,0000,,and you're seriously cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:54.34,Chiha-main,Wata,0000,0000,0000,,Interested in going out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:57.74,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,You should turn him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:09:59.37,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:00.49,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:03.36,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's a boy from a different school \Nwho knows nothing about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:04.56,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But, but!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:06.97,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time anyone's \Never asked me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:09.38,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,If I let this chance slip away, \NI might not get another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.60,0:10:11.31,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,The first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:13.13,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,That's beauty in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:15.40,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,But after spending all \Nthis time with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:17.37,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,she doesn't even seem \Nthat beautiful anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:19.34,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure that the reason nobody
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:20.98,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,from our school approaches her
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.51,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,is because she's always with Mashima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:24.07,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:27.69,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:29.31,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:31.94,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You need to experience it for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:34.11,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:34.73,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:40.11,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go out with a guy who \Nhasn't seen you play karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.47,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:46.33,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm already getting a bunch \Nof e-mails and phone calls...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:48.37,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,You gave him your number?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.03,0:10:53.71,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I blocked his number.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:54.40,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:56.16,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:57.67,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,wake up early and ride \Nthe same train as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:02.71,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,In the Tentoku Imperial Court Poetry Contest
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:10.98,card2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,2000)}Mibu no Tadami\N\NAs my love first came to realization,\Nword had already spread
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:10.98,card1,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,2000)}Taira no Kanemori\N\NSince I could not hide my love,\Npeople would always ask if \NI was pining for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:06.89,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,that was held by Emperor Murakami in 960,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:09.59,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,there were two poems that \Nwere especially beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:12.75,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,As I watch the prez, \Nthose poems come to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:16.43,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Poems about a love that \Ncannot be concealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:19.97,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,The nincompoops in our \Nclub have no clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:23.70,nin,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,nin
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:23.70,white1,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,I've \Nnever \Nblocked \Nanyone \Nbefore
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:23.70,com,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,com
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:23.70,white2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Me \Neither
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:23.70,poop,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,poop
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:23.70,white3,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye,\NWatanabe-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:23.68,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,But I understand, prez!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.53,cellphone2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya Arata - Cell \N Wataya Arata - Fukui Home
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:28.64,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been able to bring \Nmyself to send him an e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:32.04,cellphone3,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya Arata - Cell \N Wataya Arata - Fukui Home
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:31.98,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi even gave me his address...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:38.34,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Arata lost in the fourth \Nround of the Western qualifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.68,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,How does he feel right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:44.43,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,How upset is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:48.08,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many things I \Nwant to talk to him about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.55,0:11:51.51,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I need more...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:55.41,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,More practice, more effort, more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:57.44,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I was away for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:01.00,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have stopped playing \Nkaruta for a single day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:04.46,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:09.45,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Takemura-san, the Western finalist, \Nwasn't especially good,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:13.30,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,but he had the momentum of ranking \Nin four tournaments this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:15.71,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,plus the stamina to last six matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:18.88,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,The qualifiers are as \Nserious as it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:23.09,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to treat every practice \Nmatch like a real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.75,0:12:26.60,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin the third match.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.57,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Daisuke-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:30.09,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're playing Arata-kun next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:32.73,Chiha-main,Dai,0000,0000,0000,,What?  I don't wanna \Nplay him.  He's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:35.60,Chiha-main,Dai,0000,0000,0000,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:40.03,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Coach, there isn't anyone \Nleft for Wataya-kun to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:43.03,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,And Murao-kun didn't show up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:48.49,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:50.63,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,You here to tell me to come practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:52.04,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:54.70,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,That's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:57.29,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,You never used to stick your \Nnose where it didn't belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:01.45,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're the one who quit \Nkaruta for a year and a half.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:03.59,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, now you're telling \Nme I need to practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:09.23,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,I know you want to get better,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:10.64,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't help you practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:14.54,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,Say "hi" to everyone at the \NNagumo society for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:15.39,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:20.07,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:23.39,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I regret running away from karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:25.45,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,You can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:29.07,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,You can't spend too much time \Naway from karuta, Murao-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:31.91,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,You'll lose your chance \Nto become Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.39,Chiha-main,Mura,0000,0000,0000,,S-Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:40.63,scary,Mura,0000,0000,0000,,Shiver
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:38.29,Chiha-main,Mura,0000,0000,0000,,You really scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:41.99,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,The point of karuta is to become Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:47.26,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,I can no longer play \Nkaruta at that level.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:50.73,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know if you ever \Nwant to play for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:53.65,Chiha-main,Murao,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:02.84,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.97,0:14:05.65,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,to stick my nose in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:11.55,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:19.04,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan, you look happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:22.17,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,That's because there's finally \Na match in formal dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:30.26,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The Tokyo Otsuka Karuta Memorial Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:33.94,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Where the Master and Queen \Nchallenger matches are held
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:35.18,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,between the East and West finalists.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.23,0:14:39.32,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The matches are best-of-three \Nand the players wear hakama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:41.87,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The first player to achieve two wins
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:43.75,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,earns the right to challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.90,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,the Master or Queen at Omi Jingu in January.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:53.36,people,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}Master/Queen Challenger Final\NHosted by the National Karuta Association
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:53.36,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but think...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:57.13,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't lost my cool,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:59.05,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,I would be sitting there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:09.36,Chiha-internal,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,I won the East qualifier \Nbecause Dr. Harada tired out
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:12.51,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotegawa-kun in the semi-final for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:11.55,grunt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,600)}Grunt
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:18.39,Chiha-internal,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me play, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.86,luck,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Best of luck
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:33.30,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be too arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:37.85,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Could I have been sitting there \Nif I tried a little harder?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:41.92,final,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,500)}Master/Queen Challenger Final
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:41.49,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The players there represent \NEast and West Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:43.64,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We will now begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:45.92,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,They're representing us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:49.31,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:10.40,Chiha-main,Dai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:13.09,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:15.82,Chiha-main,Dai,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.94,Chiha-main,Dai,0000,0000,0000,,Arata-niichan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:23.13,Chiha-main,Dai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:24.78,Chiha-main,Dai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:28.38,Chiha-main,Dai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep playing until I'm sick of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:29.05,Chiha-main,Dai,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:33.05,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,We have our challengers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:35.19,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,The challenger for Master \Nis Takemura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:37.32,Chiha-main,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,The challenger for Queen \Nis Yamamoto Yumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:41.31,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,That was tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:45.36,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, three games \Nagainst the same opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:48.32,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Takemura-san is \Nlike an armored tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:50.93,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:52.64,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take this thing off yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:55.52,Chiha-main,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,It's completely soaked with sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:05.33,Chiha-flashback,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,The Shiranami society dream
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:08.34,Chiha-flashback,Tsubo,0000,0000,0000,,is to produce a Master one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:30.18,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:34.11,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:38.09,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be able to look back one day
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:41.14,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,and say it was all worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:45.64,Chiha-main,Hori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about you, Chi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:46.38,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:48.27,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine, Michiru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:50.51,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I placed 290th on the second term exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:52.65,Chiha-main,Hori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:53.49,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:56.13,Chiha-main,Hori,0000,0000,0000,,Chi-chan, you're spending \Nall of your time on karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.93,Chiha-main,Hori,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't there other \Nthings you need to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.38,0:18:01.38,Chiha-main,Hori,0000,0000,0000,,Like making friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:04.18,Chiha-main,Hori,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:04.18,party,Hori,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)}Class 1-2 End of Second Term  PARTY\NTime: 12/24  6:00 PM\NAt the "Italian Kitchen" next to Shinjuku Station\NEntry Fee: 2,500 yen\NDrink bar\NHosts:  Horikawa and Matsuda
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:08.72,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,A party on Christmas Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:10.37,Chiha-main,Hori,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any plans, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:12.32,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I do.  I'll be practicing karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:14.07,Chiha-main,Hori,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Ayase-san's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:15.41,Chiha-main,Hori,0000,0000,0000,,So is Komano-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:18.61,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, our class is also having a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:20.81,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Class 6 will be having a hot \Npot party on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:22.33,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Our class is going bowling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:27.83,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll take December 24th off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:29.33,Ooh,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,500)}Ooh
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.11,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase-san, that outfit's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:31.66,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:32.82,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister's a model, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:34.64,Chiha-main,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I came!  \NCan I take a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:35.37,Chiha-main,E,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:35.96,Chiha-overlap,F,0000,0000,0000,,Her legs are so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:36.84,Chiha-main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Her face is tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:37.59,Chiha-main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:40.90,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,So, the karuta club is working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:43.76,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we're in the mountain climbing club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:46.26,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,We're a boring club with \Nonly a few members,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:49.06,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,but the karuta club inspires \Nus to do the best we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:53.23,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,We compete to see who can \Nput up tents faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:54.82,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:56.83,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,When we practice in the courtyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:58.47,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,people give us funny looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:18:59.83,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:02.41,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda is the only male member \Nin the tea ceremony club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:04.04,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?  \NI get free snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:10.17,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,There are important rules to \Nfollow for a seafood hot pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:11.50,turkey,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Turkey
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:16.23,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that this was a class party,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:18.19,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,so why am I the only guy here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:20.66,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Ayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:22.92,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I got to talk to a bunch of girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:24.81,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Though, they were just asking \Nme about Mashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:26.68,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:28.94,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:31.37,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, there were a bunch of classmates
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:33.70,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I never really talked with before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.08,0:19:35.47,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:39.12,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I would be having more fun if the \Nother club members were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:48.30,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I read in a book once...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.10,0:19:51.88,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,When you find yourself wishing that \Na certain person was also here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:53.46,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,that person is like family to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:57.75,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of how long \Nor well you know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:02.80,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish that someone \Nwas also here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:05.54,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Who's joining in the karaoke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:07.47,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christmas Eve, so the \Nbars will all be packed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.11,0:20:14.23,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?  This is Wataya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.06,0:20:18.16,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.21,0:20:23.26,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:28.49,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm at the Nagumo society \NChristmas party right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.24,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Coach Kuriyama is belly dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:32.00,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,It's Chihaya, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:34.69,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:39.67,Chiha-flashback,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,The "misty bridge of magpie feathers"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:43.26,Chiha-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,spanned the river of stars which \Nseparated Orihime and Hikoboshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:47.98,Chiha-flashback,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,so the bridge brought them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:51.41,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:53.99,Chiha-main,Hori,0000,0000,0000,,Chi-chan, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.99,0:20:56.02,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Cell phones are incredible
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:20:59.40,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,like the misty bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:00.90,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:03.15,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I got to hear your voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:04.45,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:10.28,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:17.48,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,When the misty bridge of magpie \Nfeathers comes into sight,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:22.32,Chiha-poem,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,the night is nearly past
